lead_paragraph: Jordan Spieth is soaking up the atmosphere at scenic Liberty National for the start of the FedExCup playoffs, but the 20-year-old will be all business by Thursday's first round of the lucrative series.

headline.main: Spieth Leads Charge of Young Guns Into FedExCup Playoffs
